oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Wake County Fair Assocation file record sheet no 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Hatch record for the Wake County Fair Association from August to September 1929. Lists folio number, dates, items, itemized debits, total debits, and credits. Hatch printed posters for the Wake County Fair Assocation only in 1929.
